# VHS tape for podfive repack command
Output docs/images/repack.gif

Set Shell "bash"
Set FontFamily "FiraCode Nerd Font Mono"
Set FontSize 16
Set Width 900
Set Height 400
Set LetterSpacing 0
Set LineHeight 1.2
Set Padding 20
Set Theme "Dracula"
Set WindowBar Colorful
Set Margin 20
Set BorderRadius 10

Type "podfive repack data/drna/yeast_trna_reads.pod5 -o /tmp/repacked/"
Enter
Sleep 5s
